        Parameters:
        externalFeederSystems - a proxy to external services that can provide personal data (CPR register) and treatment data (EHR).

        public RegistryEntry buildRegistryEntry()
        Build a meta data / registry entry presentation of the data stored in this PHMR. The metadata is used to identify the PHMR's central searchable contents in the XDS registry so lookup of the PHMR can be made in the XDS repository
